        <mxCell id="l8XAbYTrLUXOISi5q83G-5" value="&lt;div&gt;- implement interface to various type of using&lt;/div&gt;- using a common interface but logic in business between them are different&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;-&amp;gt; violate liskov principle : hidden bug&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;-&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;call thought virtual call -&amp;gt; low&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;cost for&amp;nbsp;final/static is very quickly -&amp;gt; VM know that it is not override : inline immediately no lookup&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;dynamic dispatch :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;run-time&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;flexible for client&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;static matching :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;compile-time&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Inflexible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
